For example:  if 13 of the actions were fought against democratic govt's and only 5 were fought against nations that were some other form of gov't (just tossing numbers about to illustrate the line of questioning..not trying to give facts..), then the &quot;5 that resulted in Democracy&quot; would reflect a 100% success-rate for doing so.<br>
<br>
Similarly, for ex, if only two of those 18 were undertaken unilaterally..then Panama represents a 50% success-rate.<br>
